  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 6-7 Guests</strong></p>
<p>This delightful chalet is on the first floor of a smart building and enjoys a fantastic location, just 100m from Zermatt's church square and the bustling main street, and only 400m from the Matterhorn Glacier Express gondola for access to the superb ski area.</p>
<p>The attractive living/dining room is bright and spacious and has a lovely south-facing balcony. The comfortable bedrooms and well-appointed bath/shower rooms make this chalet the perfect spot from which to explore and enjoy all that this famous resort has to offer. Our team of reps and hosts in Zermatt look forward to welcoming you.</p>]]></description>
